                    <li><a href="/Documentation/AI_CHAT_DOCUMENTATION_FEATURE_SPEC" style="color: var(--link-color);">AI Chat Feature Specification</a> - Complete architecture including schema design</li>
                    <li><a href="/Documentation/Result_Class_Development_Guide" style="color: var(--link-color);">Result Class Development Guide</a> - Detailed patterns and examples</li>
                    <li><a href="/Documentation/DATABASE_CONNECTION_STRATEGY" style="color: var(--link-color);">Database Connection Strategy</a> - Multi-database configuration</li>
                    <li><a href="/admin" style="color: var(--link-color);">Administrative Interface</a> - Schema management tools (/admin/database_schema, /admin/compare_schema, /admin/migrate_schema)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="row" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-large); padding-top: var(--spacing-medium); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
        <div class="col-100">
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: var(--font-size-small); text-align: center;">
                For questions or contributions, see the Developer Guidelines in the in-app documentation.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
